Serenity, luxury, peace and privacy await you at this private, gated 6+ acre estate in beautiful Qualicum Beach, BC, located on a bluff overlooking the majestic Straight of Georgia, Denman, Hornby, Lasqueti and Texada Islands and the snowcapped mountains of the main land . The 5700+ sq ft 2010 built home features all the modern luxuries including granite throughout, heated tile floors, acacia hardwood up and down, breathtaking ocean views from almost every room, and upper and lower wrap around ocean-front decks. 
The 2819 sq ft upper/main floor plan is open to maximize views and is designed to be everything to its owners: The dream kitchen- with-a-view includes graite countertops, a Viking 2 oven/6 burner stove, huge central island with eating bar, a separate bar area with its own sink, and an eating nook with access to the upper deck. Adjacent, the dining and living rooms share a 2 sided fireplace and walls of windows to let in the views, also with access also to the upper deck. The oceanview master suite includes access to the wrap around deck and an ensuite with his and hers sinks and walk in closets, jetted tub and separate shower. Your guests will enjoy their own room complete with walk in closet and its own full bath. A spacious mudroom (with room for washer/dryer) is found off the 3 car garage and features built in lockers, his and hers closets and an additional utility closet. It conveniently opens to the walk through panrty, with its own fridge, recycling area and desk, with easy access to the kitchen so carrying groceries in and storing them is a breeze. 
The walk out 2000 sq ft lower level features 3 additional bedrooms for children or grandchildren all with ocean views, built in bookcases and seating areas, and walk in closets; 2 full baths; central entertainment/ family room with built in desk and entertainment unit, ocean views and access to the lower deck; wine cellar; extra large laundry/ storage room and an undeveloped storage area with access off the lower deck and from within. Atop the 3 car garage is a large 800 sq ft+bonus room which will happily house your pool table, and work out area and a seating or office area. Access is from the main floor of the home. 
The fenced and gated home is fully landscaped including front circular lighted driveway with central fountain and underground irrigation. Overlooking the ocean perched on the bluff is an all season gazebo with running water and kitchenette, also with its own deck with 180 degree views. 
Elsewhere on the property is featured a legal second 2 bedroom/ single bath home ideal for your caretaker, inlaws, additonal guests or as a source of revenue towards a mortgage, renting for $1100/ month. There is also an additional building with bachelor suite and single garage that could rent for $600/ mo, a prodcutive cherry orchard and large fenced second orchard with vegetable garden. 2013 property taxes were $4800 yr. This home is surrounded by other multi million dollar properties in prestigious Qualicum Beach, where the winters are mild and the summers are dry and warm, and real estate sales are up 21% over 2013. The Comox airport is 50 min away, Mount Washington skiing is 60 minutes away, downtown Qualicum is a 10 minute drive and Nanaimo with access to the ferry to Vancouver is 35 minutes away.
